{"tid":2377147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獄中寫信感謝支持者　胡志偉：關心及祝福是強心針","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T11:27:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3581f6776ab1d6145bc80ed2712cbe93e62357b5","tid":2377147,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/f542b7b654de551c37526589373d8b5a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210123/_2021012316182575986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2Ff542b7b654de551c37526589373d8b5a%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210123%2F_2021012316182575986.jpg&h=59a54d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡志偉在信中感激市民對他的愛護。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n民主黨前主席胡志偉涉嫌與去年多次未經批准集結有關被控，原保釋候訊，早前因違反保釋條件而被拘押。其Facebook專頁今日發文，並上傳他在獄中所撰寫的信。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉在信中感激市民對他的愛護，並指支持者的關心及祝福亦是強心針，又形容為寒冬中的暖流。他又指，《基本法》的條文遭人任意演繹，又指「誰是誰非實在無言以對」。他強調，民主從來不是賜予，對比其他付出更多的人，他所面對的困難儘管不少，但仍能應付。<br />\n<br />\n他亦指，對比其他付出更多的人，他所面對的困難儘管不少，但仍能應付。他認為，未來難以預料，亦可能會有更長及更多失去自由的日子，呼籲市民珍惜當下，以及珍惜擁有的親情、愛情、健康、友情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/st/d5817a6e4d8c17df440d069cf40b42b7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210123/_2021012316182644743.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fst%2Fd5817a6e4d8c17df440d069cf40b42b7%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210123%2F_2021012316182644743.jpg&h=5a0d4488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡志偉Fb圖片"},{"pid":"520b62b366d241bba3129b7dc53aa63fdcca41b0","tid":2377147,"uid":185424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}